original: Zachrisson, Gustaf Ragnar, kyrkoherde, Rölanda, f. 17/6/98 i Foss, Gbgs o. Boh. 1., av C. F. o. Kristina Zachrisson. G. 28 m. Signe Rosendahl. Barn: Anna f. 28, stud., Malmö, Sven 34, Erik 36, Karin 38, Nils 41. — Stud:ex i Lund 24, teol. fil. ex. 30, teol. kand., prakt. teol. prov o. prästv. f. Karlstads stift 32. V. pastor i Rölanda 32, kyrkoh. där sed. 34. Ordf. i kyrkostämma, skolstyr., barnav:nd o. kom-m :fullm.
translated: Zachrisson, Gustaf Ragnar, vicar, Rölanda, b. 17/6/98 in Foss, Gothenburg and Bohuslän, 1st child of C. F. and Kristina Zachrisson. Married on 28, with Signe Rosendahl. Children: Anna b. 28, student, Malmö, Sven b. 34, Erik b. 36, Karin b. 38, Nils b. 41. — Graduated from Lund University in 1924, Bachelor of Theology in 1930, theological candidate, practical theological examination and ordained as a priest for the Karlstad Diocese in 1932. Assistant pastor in Rölanda from 1932, became vicar there in 1934. Chairman of the church assembly, school board, child welfare committee, and municipal council.
